      {
        "path": "README.md",
        "language": "markdown",
        "preview": "# Create A Traling Stop Loss\n\nGenerated by Binary IDE as a portable `package_bundle` starter bundle.\n\n## Intent\n\nCreate a traling stop loss\n\n## Run\n\n```bash\nnpm install\nnpm run build\nnpm start\n```\n\n## Runtime\n\n- Runtime: node20\n- Platform: portable\n- Package manager: npm\n",
        "hash": "0dc0a25442599ad10ad1b50d0967a7492f26e5146210fadd3681dd32718c9366",
        "completed": true,
